==English==
===Noun===
'''[[inorganic]] [[polymer]]'''
#{{chemistry}} any [[giant molecule]] linked by [[covalent bond]]s, but having no (or few) [[carbon]] [[atom]]s in the main [[molecular]] [[backbone]]
===Usage notes===
* [[carbon fibre]]s, [[graphite]] and [[diamond]] are, however, considered to be inorganic polymers
